// PopHelp - Sheet PH_1800, Row 76, POP_HELP_XPDEBT 
// DisplayTitle :
"P449848828" "XP Debt"
// DisplayText :
"P2583218963" "<face heading><span align=center><color orange>Experience Debt</color></span></face><br><br>When you are defeated, you incur <color turquoise>experience debt</color>. While this debt remains, you must spend half your earned experience paying it off. The rest of your experience accumulates normally. Your debt will never exceed more than half the experience points required for your next security level."
// ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// PopHelp - Sheet PH_NTutorial, Row 4, CODEPH_NTUTORIAL1 
// DisplayTitle :
"P229373857" "Movement"
// DisplayText :
"P878660661" "<br><br><face heading><span align=center><color DeepSkyBlue>Movement</color></face><br>Get out of Galaxy City!<br><br>Use the W, A, S, & D keys to move</span><span align=center><img src=NPopHelpKeyboard.tga></span><span align=center>and SPACEBAR to jump!</span><span align=center><img src=NPopHelpSpaceBar.tga></span>"
// ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// PopHelp - Sheet PH_NTutorial, Row 5, POP_HELP_NTUTORIAL2 
// DisplayTitle :
"P346931487" "Compass Markers"
// DisplayText :
"P4000418530" "<face heading><span align=center><color DeepSkyBlue>Compass Markers</color></face><br><bR>Follow the compass marker to find a way out!"
// ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// PopHelp - Sheet PH_NTutorial, Row 6, POP_HELP_NTUTORIAL3 
// DisplayText :
"P4058535375" "<face heading><span align=center><color DeepSkyBlue>Mission Doors</color></face><br><br><color yellow>Right click</color> on the door to enter it. <span align=center><img src=Tut_P_MissionDoor.tga>"
// ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// PopHelp - Sheet PH_NTutorial, Row 7, POP_HELP_NTUTORIAL4 
// DisplayTitle :
"P2331895470" "Combat"
// DisplayText :
"P1257561543" "<br><br><span align=center><face heading><color DeepSkyBlue>Combat</color></face><br>Defeat the Shivans by left clicking on the powers in your power tray!<br><br>You can also activate your power using the number beside it!<br><span align=center><img src=NPopHelpCombat.tga></scale>"
// ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// PopHelp - Sheet PH_NTutorial, Row 8, POP_HELP_NTUTORIAL5 
// DisplayTitle :
"P1964947751" "Inspirations"
// DisplayText :
"P1994499592" "<span align=center><face heading><color DeepSkyBlue>Inspirations</color></face><br><br>You're hurt! Left click on your inspiration tray to heal yourself.<br><br>You can get inspirations by defeating enemies and also in stores within the world."
// ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// PopHelp - Sheet PH_NTutorial, Row 9, POP_HELP_NTUTORIAL6 
// DisplayTitle :
"P1120787796" "Dialog"
// DisplayText :
"P3183886131" "<br><br><span align=center><face heading><color DeepSkyBlue>NPC Interaction</color><br></face><br>Left click on an NPC to interact with it.<br><br><img src=NPopHelpTrainerHero.tga>"
// ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// PopHelp - Sheet PH_NTutorial, Row 10, POP_HELP_NTUTORIAL6_Villain 
// DisplayText :
"P331513802" "<br><br><span align=center><face heading><color DeepSkyBlue>NPC Interaction</color><br></face><br>Left click on an NPC to interact with it.<br><br><img src=NPopHelpTrainerVillain.tga>"
// ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// PopHelp - Sheet PH_NTutorial, Row 11, POP_HELP_NTUTORIAL7 
// DisplayTitle :
"P2427297954" "Moral Choice"
// DisplayText :
"P2751899917" "<span align=center><face heading><color DeepSkyBlue>Moral Choice</color></face><br><br>You must choose your alignment!<br><br> Are you a <color DeepSkyblue>Hero</color> or a <color red>Villain</color>?"
// ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// PopHelp - Sheet PH_NTutorial, Row 12, POP_HELP_NTUTORIAL8_Hero 
// DisplayTitle :
"P4152644891" "Zone Events"
// DisplayText :
"P3658388964" "<br><br><span align=center><face heading><color DeepSkyBlue>Zone Events</color><br></face><br>You're entering a zone event.<br><br>Players can work together to complete objectives in the event.<br><img src=NPopHelpZoneEvent.tga>"
// ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// PopHelp - Sheet PH_NTutorial, Row 13, POP_HELP_NTUTORIAL8_Villain 
// ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// PopHelp - Sheet PH_NTutorial, Row 14, NONE 
// DisplayText :
"P1079057898" "<br><br><span align=center><face heading><color DeepSkyBlue>Jumping</color><br></face><br>Get a running start to jump over the chasm!<br><br>Press SPACEBAR to jump!"
// ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// PopHelp - Sheet PH_NTutorial, Row 15, POP_HELP_FIRSTMISSION 
// DisplayTitle :
"P67814311" "Instanced Missions"
// DisplayText :
"P2492773275" "<br><br><span align=center><face heading><color DeepSkyBlue>Instanced Missions</color><br><br></face><br>You're now inside of an instanced mission.<br><br> This is your own private mission, but you can invite other people to join you.<br><br> The more players you have with you, the more enemies will show up!"
// ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// PopHelp - Sheet PH_NTutorial, Row 16, POP_HELP_NTUTORIAL8_Waypoint 
// DisplayTitle :
"P66265670" "Waypoints"
// DisplayText :
"P506536845" "<br><br><span align=center><face heading><color DeepSkyBlue>Waypoints</color><br></face><br>Waypoints can help direct you towards your next destination. They may be behind or above your character.<br><br>Move to your next waypoint now to look for the Blue Spectrum!<br><br><img src=NPopHelpWaypointMarkert.tga>"
// ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// PopHelp - Sheet PH_2100, Row 4, POP_HELP_CLUEINFO 
// DisplayText :
"P3810964639" "<br><br><span align=center><face heading><color DeepSkyBlue>Clues</color><br><br></face><br>You've received a clue!<br><br>Clues reveal more information on the current story you are on.<br><br>Click on CLUES on your navigation bar to see what you found!"
// ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// PopHelp - Sheet PH_2100, Row 5, POP_HELP_CELLINFO 
// DisplayTitle :
"P424348685" "Cellphones"
// DisplayText :
"P2300287982" "<br><br><span align=center><face heading><color DeepSkyBlue>Cellphones</color><br><br></face><br>You have the ability to call your contact up!<br><br>Click on CONTACTS, then select CALL in order to speak with them."
// ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// PopHelp - Sheet PH_2100, Row 6, POP_HELP_ELEVATORS 
// DisplayTitle :
"P641512533" "Elevators"
// DisplayText :
"P3615292236" "<br><br><span align=center><face heading><color DeepSkyBlue>Elevators</color><br><br></face><br>You can use elevators to reach other levels within the map. Left click on the door to move yourself to the next level."
// ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// PopHelp - Sheet PH_2400, Row 4, POP_HELP_ALLIES 
// DisplayTitle :
"P3463767382" "Allies"
// DisplayText :
"P296647680" "<br><br><face heading><span align=center><color DeepSkyBlue>Movement</color></face><br>Mission Allies<br><br>You have a special type of ally in this mission!<br><br>This ally will not go away when they're defeated; instead, they will rest for some time, then get back up to full health.</span><span align=center><img src=NPopHelpZoneEvent.tga></span>"
// ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

